summary: ...HUMBERTO A LITTLE STRONGER AND EXPECTED TO PRODUCE DANGEROUS SURF FOR BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK... ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE IN BERMUDA ON TUESDAY... As of 8:00 AM AST Mon Sep 29 the center of Humberto was located near 27.5, -67.3 with movement NW at 14 mph. The minimum central pressure was 938 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 145 mph.
